sl7-sensors (1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release: SSC sensor bring-up for the Surface Laptop 7 —
    sensors-PD FastRPC file service feeding the DSP registry the sensor
    configuration extracted from the machine's Windows partition,
    net.hadess.SensorProxy daemon with optional direct backlight
    controller, and the unified sl7-sensors CLI (setup, lux, color, mode,
    status).

